                                2002 - index
       National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration Current Events

   OSEI fire products include multichannel color composite imagery and
   single-channel grayscale imagery of wildfire and controlled burn
   events. Products in this event group show smoke (FSM), hotspots (FHS)
   or both (FSMHS) from the fires.

   Other sites of interest:
     * Satellite Services Division Experimental Fire Analysis Page
     * NESDIS Office of Research and Applications Automated Fire Mapping
       System Page

